value.value: Mixing of dry ingredients with the addition of a small amount of liquid, done to increase binding capability.
Mixing of dry ingredients by mechanical agitation within a containment zone.

Mixing of solids into liquid or of immiscible liquids by shear and impact within high velocity streams.
Mixing of solids into liquid, without appreciable size reduction, to form a stable suspension.
Mixing of miscible liquids to form a homogeneous solution.
Any mixing operation not otherwise specified.
